{"lemma":"فاحِش","slug":"فاحِش","root":"ف.ح.ش","root_slug":"ف-ح-ش","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ح-ش","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n33128"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D8%A7%D8%AD%D9%90%D8%B4"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to engage in obscene dialogue with, to vie with (someone) in vulgar talk","tags":["Classical"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"grievous, glaring, outrageous, flagrant, abominable, exorbitant, onerous","tags":["Classical"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"obscene, indecent, lewd, offensive, vulgar","tags":["Classical"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Derived from the active participle of فَحُشَ (faḥuša, “to become obscene”)."},"ipa":["/faː.ħa.ʃa/","/faː.ħiʃ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33128","headword_ar":"فَاحِشٌ","root":"fH$","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"Anything, (Msb, TA,) or any evil thing, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excessive, immoderate, enormous, exorbitant, beyond measure, exceeding the proper bounds"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limits,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overmuch:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA:) anything"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not agreeable with truth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with rule"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"measure:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foul, evil, bad, abominable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unseemly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gross, immodest, lewd,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obscene;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] applied to a thing or an affair, (Mgh, Msb,) and to speech or language. (TA.) It is said in a trad., He was asked respecting the blood of fleas, [whether it rendered a garment impure,] and said"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ino lamo yakuno faAHi$FA falaA baA^osa bihi","text_ar":"اـِنْ لَمْ يَكُنْ فَاحِشًا فَلَا بَاْسَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"If it is not excessive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beyond measure, there is no harm in it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who transgresses the proper bounds"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limits"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in anything:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and particularly]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in speech"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"language,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in reply:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who is foul, evil, bad, abominable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unseemly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gross, immodest, lewd,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obscene;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in speech"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"language,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in action:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faH~aA$N","text_ar":"فَحَّاشٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same;"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2345},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * A, * Mgh;) or has an intensive signification: (TA:) pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuHa$aA='u","text_ar":"فُحَشَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"juhalaA='u","text_ar":"جُهَلَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAhilN","text_ar":"جَاهِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", since"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuHo$","text_ar":"فُحْش"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a sort of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jahol","text_ar":"جَهْل"},{"kind":"text","text":", and contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hilom","text_ar":"حِلْم"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IJ.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA","text_ar":"لَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"takuwniY faAHi$apF","text_ar":"تَكُونِى فَاحِشَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Be not thou a trangressor of the proper bounds"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limits in reply:"},{"kind":"text","text":"which words were addressed to 'Áïsheh: (K, TA:) but accord. to one relation, the words were"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taquwliY","text_ar":"لَا تَقُولِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAHi$apF","text_ar":"فَاحِشَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAHi$apN","text_ar":"فَاحِشَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below.] ―         -b3-  A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil in disposition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IB.) ―         -b4-  A man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"niggardly, tenacious,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"avaricious:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"very niggardly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excessively,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inordinately, so."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","TA","S","O","K","Mgh","A"]}]}}